Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.34,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,A checkout can look finished
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:04.37,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,and still stop a keyboard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:06.41,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,user cold. AccessPatch EU turns
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:08.44,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,that failure into an evidence-backed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.48,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,patch, then proves the same
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.51,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,journey works. This is the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.55,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,real synthetic Lattice Supply checkout
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:16.58,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,on localhost. I open secure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:18.62,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,checkout and use only the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:20.65,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,keyboard. Every Tab is intercepted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.69,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,and returned to the invalid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.72,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,email. Five presses later, focus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.76,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,has not moved. The payment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.79,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,control is unnamed, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.83,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,visible error is silent to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.86,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,assistive technology. Now I run
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.90,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,npm run demo colon verify.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.93,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,This is genuine process output.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.97,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,The script resets the fixture,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.00,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,starts the app, captures before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:43.04,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,evidence, writes deterministic proposals, installs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:45.07,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,the frozen repair, scans again,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.11,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,verifies the journey, and restores
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:49.14,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,the original source bytes. The
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:51.18,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,evidence pack contains a screenshot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.21,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,sanitized DOM and accessibility data,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.25,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,a keyboard trace, and source
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:57.29,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,hints. It produces three stable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.32,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,findings: A P E U
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.36,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,zero zero one and zero
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.39,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,zero two are critical; zero
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:05.43,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,zero three is serious. External
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.46,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,requests are blocked and stored
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:09.50,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,form values are scrubbed. For
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.53,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,judges, this path is labeled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.57,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,deterministic fixture with approval actor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:15.60,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,test fixture. It needs no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.64,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,login and never pretends a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.67,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,person approved it. Separately, the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.71,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,interactive workflow runs inside signed-in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.74,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,Codex. GPT-5.6 proposes bounded candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:25.78,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,changes, but cannot approve them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:27.81,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,or decide whether they pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:29.85,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,Every edit is limited to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:31.88,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,source slash checkout slash CheckoutPage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.92,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,dot T S X. The
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:35.95,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,real diff removes the Tab
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.99,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,trap, names the payment action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:40.02,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,Confirm and pay forty-two euros,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.06,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,connects the error with aria
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:44.09,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,described by, adds alert and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:46.13,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,aria live semantics, and focuses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.16,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,the invalid email. The allowlist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.20,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,rejects every other file. AccessPatch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.24,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,replays the same Playwright journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.27,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,Tab advances, the payment action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:56.31,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,exposes its name, invalid input
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:58.34,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,is announced, and a valid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.38,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,keyboard submission reaches order confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.41,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,Deterministic checks, not the model,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:04.45,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,decide the outcome. The receipt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.48,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,is real: two critical and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:08.52,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,one serious blocker are resolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.55,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,no new serious or critical
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.59,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,regression appears, keyboard checkout passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.62,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,and the diff stays inside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.66,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,the approved root. The demo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.69,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,then restores the broken fixture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.73,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,byte for byte, keeping the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.76,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,repository repeatable while the dashboard
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:24.80,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,retains genuine before and after
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.83,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,evidence. To judge it, run
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.87,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,npm ci, install Playwright Chromium,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.90,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,then run npm run demo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.94,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,colon verify. The terminal ends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:34.97,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,with AccessPatch verification: pass. This
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.01,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,route needs no OpenAI Platform
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.04,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,API key; the interactive route
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.08,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,uses signed-in Codex. AccessPatch EU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.11,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,provides technical evidence, not legal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.15,AccessPatch,,0,0,0,,advice, certification, or guaranteed compliance.
